album.title: The Crazy World of Screamin' Jay Hawkins

track.name: Frenzy
comments: I can't help but giggle... so crazy and uninhibited...
this bloke is a nutter but good
I love his spluttering sound effects.
Yes indeed......motorboating....just add alcohol and magic happens!
Used to spectacular effect in an old "X-Files" episode, and if you think it's cool on vinyl, I heard the cat do this live, and it set off the smoke detector! *laughs*
He is one crazy mofo... and I'm okay with that :)
i was reading somewhere that the clash had him open up for them on one of their first america tours.
this love gushes from my heart, like water from the spout *perfectly imitates the sound of a spout*
